OL,3,CNI Water workers set to strike next
OL,4,Cweek
OL,6,FMembers of the Unite union who work
OL,7,Ffor Northern Ireland Water are set to
OL,8,Ftake industrial action next week.
OL,10,FWorkers have warned that full strike
OL,11,Faction could follow before Christmas
OL,12,Fif a dispute over pay is not resolved.
OL,14,FThe union has said other civil service
OL,15,Fworkers received a pay uplift 21
OL,16,Fmonths ago, and have branded the delay
OL,17,Ffor them as 'a disgrace'.
