OL,3,CNI Water workers set to strike next
OL,4,Cweek
OL,6,FNI Water employees are the only civil
OL,7,Fservice workforce who have yet to
OL,8,Freceive a five percent pay increase
OL,9,Fand #1,500 one-off payment from the
OL,10,F2023-24 tax year.
OL,12,FThe Union has written to Finance
OL,13,FMinister Caoimhe Archibald to demand
OL,14,Fshe urgently approve the pay increase
OL,15,Fto avoid the prospect of industrial
OL,16,Faction.
OL,18,FUnite regional officer Joanne
OL,19,FMcWilliams said: "Our members play a
OL,20,Fvital role in ensuring the supply of
OL,21,Fsafe drinking water.
